      "title": "Use the given function value",
      "content": "Substitute $x=9$ and $f(9)=54$ into $f(x)=6x+b$.<br/>$$54=6(9)+b$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve for b",
      "content": "Simplify and subtract $54$ from both sides.<br/>$$54=54+b$$<br/>$$b=0$$<br/>The answer is <strong>A</strong>."
